title: Celebrity Gossip- Giving Up Accounting To Act
description: One Marvel star got fired from his well paying stable job then had to lie to his parents until he got his foot in the door. Plus, Jennifer Aniston says there was one common fear that came out when A-list guest stars were filming episodes of Friends.
